MARKETING | ART DIRECTION | EDM | DIGITAL | SOCIAL

Led a comprehensive brand revitalization for Justice Haircare, an Australian-born, salon-quality haircare line known for its nature-inspired formulations and accessible luxury. Through strategic art direction, digital design, and campaign development, the project amplified the brand's presence across eCommerce platforms, social media, and email marketing. By crafting cohesive visual narratives and engaging content, the initiative enhanced customer engagement and reinforced Justice Haircare's position as a go-to choice for professional-grade haircare solutions.
